casebody.data:
PAINTER-JAMIESON
v.
PAINTER. No. 207P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 24, 2004. Robert L. Inge, Salisbury, for Deborah Woodward Painter.

The following order has been entered on the joint motion filed on the 4th day of June 2004 by Plaintiff and Defendant to Withdraw Petition (for Discretionary Review):

"Motion Allowed. By order of the Court in conference this the 24th day of June 2004."
